    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Ricinus dalgleishi. 1, dorso-ventral views of head. 2, dorso-ventral views of abdomen. 3, male genitalia. 4, mandibles. 5, labium. 6, ventro-dorsal views of thorax." ;
